wdi-DT.ODA.ODAT.XP.ZS.def: Net official development assistance is disbursement flows (net of repayment of principal) that meet the DAC definition of ODA and are made to countries and territories on the DAC list of aid recipients.
wdi-DT.ODA.ODAT.XP.ZS.name: Net ODA received
wdi-DT.ODA.ODAT.XP.ZS.source: Development Assistance Committee of the Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development, Geographical Distribution of Financial Flows to Developing Countries, Development Co-operation Report, and International Development Statistics database. Data are available online at: www.oecd.org/dac/stats/idsonline. IMF central government expense estimates are used for the denominator.
